metadata.name: Awaken
metadata.description: AWAKEN is an art piece created by Jon Encarnacion in collaboration with the very talented 3d modeler, John Muniz. This was created using one of my favorite photographs from my collection. I’ve been working on this piece for a few months now and I am very excited to present this. One of my passions is bringing my architectural photographs to life. Using my photograph as the base layer, I’ve breathed life into it by adding motion, color, and sound. My hope with this piece is to bring an overwhelming sense of inspiration to all who view it. This piece is the first of a new collection I will be creating over the course of this year. Please enjoy “AWAKEN”
